claim.claim-text:
1. A semiconductor device comprising:
a first conductive layer over an insulating surface;
an insulating layer over the first conductive layer;
a second conductive layer over the insulating layer;
a structural layer over the insulating layer;
a third conductive layer on a bottom surface of the structural layer;
wherein the second conductive layer faces the third conductive layer with a space therebetween,
wherein a part of the bottom surface of the structural layer is in contact with the insulating layer, and
wherein one lateral surface of the structural layer faces the other lateral surface of the structural layer with the space therebetween.

8. A semiconductor device comprising:
a first conductive layer over an insulating surface;
an insulating layer over the first conductive layer;
a second conductive layer over the insulating layer;
a structural layer over the insulating layer;
a third conductive layer on a bottom surface of the structural layer;
a fourth conductive layer on the bottom surface of the structural layer,
wherein the second conductive layer faces the fourth conductive layer with a space therebetween,
wherein the first conductive layer faces the third conductive layer with the space and the insulating layer therebetween,
wherein a part of the bottom surface of the structural layer is in contact with the insulating layer, and
wherein one lateral surface of the structural layer faces the other lateral surface of the structural layer with the space therebetween.
